  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK805">
<l>pētaimai yoṉṟō peruṅkiḻamai yeṉṟuṇarka</l>
<l>nōtakka naṭṭār ceyiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If friends should perform what is painful, understand that it is owing not only to ignorance, but also to the strong claims of intimacy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
